# Build context = repo ROOT. Keep the image small + reproducible: ship only
# core/ app/ web/ + the docker shell + the danmu template seed. Runtime data
# (config.json / cookie.txt / aniGamer.db / logs / output) comes from the mounted
# /app/data volume, NOT baked into the image.

# --- never ship ---
.git
.gitignore
.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
*.egg-info
build
dist

# --- desktop / Windows-only shell + launchers (not used in the container) ---
src
archived
shells/desktop.py
*.bat

# --- docs / samples / screenshots (not needed at runtime) ---
docs
*.md

# --- runtime data: comes from the mounted volume, not the image ---
# Exclude everything under data/ EXCEPT the danmu template asset, which the
# Dockerfile copies to a seed path and the entrypoint seeds into the volume.
data
!data/DanmuTemplate.ass

# --- editor / OS cruft ---
.idea
.vscode
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
